stimulus: Welcome to the experiment. Press any key to begin.

In this experiment, you will see a basketball bouncing on the screen.

Your task is to press the spacebar in sync with the moment the ball reaches the lowest point of its bounce.

Try to be as precise as possible, keeping your taps in rhythm with the ball's motion.

The experiment consists of 6 trials which all have the same bouncing velocity.

Press any key to proceed.
